{"tid":1029032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經歷3段婚姻苦命漢 指責妻子「唔執衫」捱斬","createTime":"2019-02-20T02:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T03:23:14.000Z","uid":56881,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd87eb7bb145bf039dc75c6b3c68ea789ba27b79","tid":1029032,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T02:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B73%E6%AE%B5%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB%E8%8B%A6%E5%91%BD%E6%BC%A2-%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8C%E5%94%94%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%AB%E3%80%8D%E6%8D%B1%E6%96%AC-231825872.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25AD%25B73%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25A7%25BB%25E8%258B%25A6%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%258D%25B1%25E6%2596%25AC-231825872.html&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8w%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=6365687d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B73%E6%AE%B5%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB%E8%8B%A6%E5%91%BD%E6%BC%A2-%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8C%E5%94%94%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%AB%E3%80%8D%E6%8D%B1%E6%96%AC-231825872.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IhdoUdyJE2S11tcCC0PGzw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/99a527275e5eb89a6536419de613e1ef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIhdoUdyJE2S11tcCC0PGzw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F99a527275e5eb89a6536419de613e1ef&h=314b9c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n躁妻持菜刀傷丈夫被捕。(梁裔楠攝)<br />\n更多<br />\n元宵佳節何文田發生妻子斬傷丈夫傷人案，昨日(19日)晚上10時許，一名60歲姓梁男子，收工返回愛民邨衛民樓住所，發現家中雜物凌亂，出言指責其42歲姓薄妻子「唔執衫」，2人繼而互相指罵，薄婦情緒激動，憤然衝入廚房拿起菜刀揮舞，混亂中，梁肩、手及腳受傷，他搶奪菜刀後踩在地上，報警求助。警方接報到場，經調查後，以涉嫌傷人將薄婦拘捕，梁由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，姓梁男事主原籍廣州，他於70年代移居香港，其後開店舖賣成衣至今。梁經歷了3段婚姻，躁妻原籍內地，為其第3任妻子，現在酒樓任職，2人於17年前註冊結婚，育有一對17歲大的孖女，現一家六口居於上址，另2孩為前妻所生。<br />\n<br />\n梁髮妻為香港人，因性格不合而分開，2人有一對子女，現已30餘歲。第2任妻子則為廣州人，結婚10年後其妻來港相聚，疑不習慣在港生活，1個月後突不辭而別，並失去聯絡，梁隨後返回廣州自行辦理離婚手續，梁對自己經歷3段婚姻苦笑道：「唔係多姿多采，係命苦!」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n娶埋幾個大6雞落黎<br />\n走左去仲要問點解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c3003b3248ceb1e673da413dcb605a7a98255d","tid":1029032,"uid":83609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"第二三任都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c80f8aeb2fe18823aef9ffb4a0ffef90bb249de","tid":1029032,"uid":56205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"睇topic都估到咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a7687b409bfbf6a44a607c9703f98b79fdd7aa","tid":1029032,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"問下點解你無香港人要 要返去娶大陸雞啦<br />\n有問題個個係你自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e36ad14777bfbca30efd4a6d872b71e868f541","tid":1029032,"uid":76793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"好就女人<br />\n唔好就累人<br />\n<br />\n臭雞"}]}